# Blind-review hygiene — NEVER commit author identity into the review pack.
# Real authors live in paper/authors.private.md and are introduced only at camera-ready.
paper/authors.private.md
**/authors.private.md
**/*.private.md

# Paper-enhancer phase outputs are tracked scaffold artifacts for NEE-1254.
# Keep arbitrary local scratch out, but allow the committed phase markdown files.
paper/*
